{"tid":1595342,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傳10.1前警方最高武力，香港將變成「準警方管治區」！","createTime":"2019-09-26T04:06:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T04:35:43.000Z","uid":219007,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c7e534255a3eedd68f3cc25ee561a76b115b36bf","tid":1595342,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T04:06:12.000Z","msg":"警方濫捕濫暴無日無之，更愈趨加劇，有「守護孩子」成員遭警員拖入後巷腳踢，陳伯亦被迎面噴射胡椒噴霧。獨立記者Richard Scotford今日在facebook發帖，指收到非常可靠的消息透露9月27日至10月1日期間，香港將變成「準警方管治區」，稱警方已獲授權對「不喜歡的事」以零容忍、「最高程度攻擊策略」對待，警員將用最高武力對付以任何原因集結的人群，估計或會與具攻擊性的撐中人士合作。Richard指警方目的是想令市民感到恐懼，令10.1不會有大批人上街。Richard建議抗爭者結集一起保護自己，並採取游擊戰術，制定明確目標及逃生計劃。<br />\n<br />\n民陣將在10.1舉行「國殤遊行」，並呼籲市民當日「全民着黑衣」，已向警方就遊行申請不反對通知書，但不予寄望，民陣指若警方批出反對通知書，無奈要取消遊行集會，但相信難阻大量人士上街。"},{"pid":"a66efc6fd34e348aa972c1b68c0e74487d470d29","tid":1595342,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T04:06:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190926/60085765?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190926%2F60085765%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRhZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=e3864d31\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190926%2F60085765%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=9aaf4750\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190926/60085765?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"7d304b7f1354d0dd08bd6c919821eadf20e1abb5","tid":1595342,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":1,"scor